You'll have to see them with me.

86
00:09:07,104 --> 00:09:11,334
These people are
Goryeo's rotten roots.

87
00:09:12,724 --> 00:09:16,504
But their names alone
aren't enough as evidence.

88
00:09:16,504 --> 00:09:18,784
There's a pact to kill the First King

89
