No middlemen will give
us advance payments.

96
00:10:22,984 --> 00:10:25,664
Pungwoo Trading Company is too powerful.

97
00:10:27,664 --> 00:10:28,664
Yool.

98
00:10:31,424 --> 00:10:34,104
Has anyone agreed to
a credit transaction?

99
00:10:35,504 --> 00:10:37,164
Us neither.

100
00:10:37,164 --> 00:10:38,444
Nothing is working out.

101
00:10:38,904 --> 00:10:39,804
Right.

102
00:10:40,184 --> 00:10:42,104
Did you hear the news, Miss?

103
00:10:42,364 --> 00:10:45,624
Last night, the virtuous men infiltrated
Wang Sik Ryeom's house.

104
00:10:46,804 --> 00:10:49,024
What are you talking about?

105
00:10:49,024 --> 00:10:51,964
They mobilized the palatial soldiers
and they pursued them.

106
00:10:52,224 --> 00:10:54,894
So were they captured or hurt?

107
00:10:54,894 --> 00:10:55,864
No.

108
00:10:56,144 --> 00:10:57,594
They said they ran away safely.

109
00:11:00,844 --> 00:11:02,204
Is anyone here?

110
00:11:04,604 --> 00:11:05,884
Why is that guy here?

111
00:11:05,884 --> 00:11:07,284
And who's that person beside him?

112
00:11:12,424 --> 00:11:14,684
- What brings you here?
- Yes, Shin Yool.

113
00:11:15,684 --> 00:11:17,404
Mr. Yang is here too, I see.

114
00:11:18,544 --> 00:11:19,864
Say hello.

115
00:11:19,864 --> 00:11:23,704
He runs everything at
Pungwoo Trading Co.

116
00:11:23,704 --> 00:11:24,664
Never mind.

117
00:11:25,004 --> 00:11:26,324
What brings you here?

118
00:11:26,324 --> 00:11:28,164
- You're done with us.
- What do you mean?

119
00:11:28,844 --> 00:11:32,224
All of your wealth was given
to Pungwoo Trading Co.

120
00:11:32,644 --> 00:11:34,564
but why are you still here?

121
00:11:36,324 --> 00:11:38,404
You want us to hand over our homes?

122
00:11:38,404 --> 00:11:41,344
You need to move out,
so that we can move in.

123
00:11:43,964 --> 00:11:44,814
That's ridiculous!

124
00:11:44,814 --> 00:11:46,324
Give us some time.

125
00:11:46,684 --> 00:11:48,764
Then we'll pay for our land here.

126
00:11:48,764 --> 00:11:50,664
You have 15 days.

127
00:11:50,664 --> 00:11:52,624
If you don't pay within 15 days,

128
00:11:53,444 --> 00:11:54,784
you'll have to leave.

129
00:11:55,184 --> 00:11:56,284
Look here!

130
00:11:56,284 --> 00:11:58,684
- How could we do that in 15 days?
- If we pay,

131
00:11:59,084 --> 00:12:01,964
then this land
and the house is ours.

132
00:12:01,964 --> 00:12:03,394
You've promised.

133
00:12:03,394 --> 00:12:05,464
How can we get the money in 15 days?

134
00:12:06,384 --> 00:12:08,564
Now we're really going down!

135
00:12:09,764 --> 00:12:10,984
Miss.

136
00:12:11,324 --> 00:12:13,374
Is there a way for our
company to survive?

137
00:12:14,644 --> 00:12:17,504
It's not impossible.

138
00:12:21,064 --> 00:12:22,314
What is it?

139
00:12:22,584 --> 00:12:25,854
We need to get the spices
that are being delivered on the ship.

140
00:12:26,764 --> 00:12:29,624
The spices do yield a lot of money.

141
00:12:29,624 --> 00:12:33,084
The prices of spices have skyrocketed
in the central districts.

142
00:12:33,384 --> 00:12:35,464
It's probably risen more than 10 fold.

143
00:12:35,464 --> 00:12:38,764
With that money, we
can pay for our house,

144
00:12:39,164 --> 00:12:40,894
and we'll have seed money as well.

145
00:12:41,224 --> 00:12:44,634
But you said we need
30,000 ginseng roots.

146
00:12:44,984 --> 00:12:49,064
There is one person in the capital

147
00:12:50,284 --> 00:12:51,944
who has 30,000 ginseng roots.

148
00:12:53,084 --> 00:12:54,924
Who is it?

149
00:12:55,704 --> 00:12:57,264
It's Princess Yeo Won.

150
00:12:58,744 --> 00:13:00,184
Miss.

151
00:13:00,544 --> 00:13:03,124
So you're going to meet her right now?

152
00:13:03,704 --> 00:13:05,984
She's Prince Wang So's wife!

153
00:13:05,984 --> 00:13:07,784
Do you think she'll help us?

154
00:13:07,784 --> 00:13:10,084
We'll be lucky if she
doesn't treat us badly!

155
00:13:10,084 --> 00:13:11,064
I'm against it, too.

156
00:13:11,064 --> 00:13:12,364
It won't work anyway.

157
00:13:12,364 --> 00:13:15,924
I hate all of the Hwang family!

158
00:14:20,084 --> 00:14:21,784
Gaebong!

159
00:14:24,784 --> 00:14:27,844
Don't worry, you fool!

160
00:14:27,844 --> 00:14:30,984
Everything will be returned.

161
00:14:31,384 --> 00:14:33,764
The world's most interesting goods

162
00:14:33,764 --> 00:14:37,644
will be stocked in
the magical storage room,

163
00:14:37,644 --> 00:14:39,024
and at this inn,

164
00:14:39,024 --> 00:14:42,944
Goryeo's, I mean,
all the world's men

165
00:14:42,944 --> 00:14:47,544
will come here and make a ruckus.

166
00:14:47,544 --> 00:14:50,044
Chunghae Trading Co.
is no ordinary company.

167
00:14:50,044 --> 00:14:51,744
Don't worry.

168
00:14:55,164 --> 00:14:56,404
What are you doing?

169
00:14:56,404 --> 00:14:58,364
- Are you okay?
- What are you talking about?

170
00:14:58,364 --> 00:14:59,784
Didn't you get hurt

171
00:14:59,784 --> 00:15:01,684
when the soldiers chased after you?

172
00:15:01,684 --> 00:15:05,504
My shoulder, my back!

173
00:15:06,084 --> 00:15:07,604
Even my legs!

174
00:15:11,904 --> 00:15:13,444
Does it hurt a lot?

175
00:15:13,764 --> 00:15:15,284
Of course it does!

176
00:15:15,284 --> 00:15:17,654
- Not there, but a little lower.
- Here?

177
00:15:19,024 --> 00:15:20,424
Or…

178
00:15:21,224 --> 00:15:22,724
Or here?

179
00:15:22,724 --> 00:15:26,224
You keep touching where
it hurts, go left.

180
00:15:26,224 --> 00:15:27,404
Go right!

181
00:15:27,904 --> 00:15:29,384
Yeah, a little lower.

182
00:15:29,864 --> 00:15:31,194
Go a little lower.

183
00:15:33,004 --> 00:15:34,384
Why did you hit me?

184
00:15:34,804 --> 00:15:36,844
I don't think you got hurt.

185
00:15:36,844 --> 00:15:38,574
What do you mean?

186
00:15:39,534 --> 00:15:41,364
I wasn't hurt at all.

187
00:15:42,664 --> 00:15:46,744
- *<i>Hyungnim!
- Why are you so gullible?

188
00:15:42,664 --> 00:15:46,744
