You don't need to thank me.

274
00:20:37,404 --> 00:20:42,544
Goryeo needed to defeat the Khitans too.

275
00:20:45,064 --> 00:20:46,664
But

276
00:20:47,884 --> 00:20:49,904
you speak the language of Goryeo.

277
00:20:52,884 --> 00:20:55,244
Thanks to one Goryeo man,

278
00:20:56,104 --> 00:20:58,844
I became furious and
learned the language.

279
00:20:59,844 --> 00:21:02,604
That man must have some guts

280
00:21:03,064 --> 00:21:05,264
to make the great General Gwak furious.

281
00:21:05,264 --> 00:21:07,644
Should we catch and put
him to death for you?

282
00:21:10,324 --> 00:21:14,094
So, what is your request?

283
00:21:14,094 --> 00:21:15,164
Father.

284
00:21:16,624 --> 00:21:19,944
General Gwak is going to
attack his surroundings

285
00:21:20,264 --> 00:21:22,524
so he can establish a nation
in the central districts.

286
00:21:22,524 --> 00:21:25,044
He's planning a blitz attack,

287
00:21:25,624 --> 00:21:27,904
so he needs you to provide the soldiers.

288
00:21:28,304 --> 00:21:31,944
So please let me meet the King.

289
00:21:32,444 --> 00:21:34,384
I will persuade him.

290
00:21:35,244 --> 00:21:36,784
Well

291
00:21:37,924 --> 00:21:41,404
you don't need to meet the King.

292
00:21:42,224 --> 00:21:46,084
He's not in stable
mental health right now.

293
00:21:47,124 --> 00:21:49,824
He can't make any judgments.

294
00:21:56,844 --> 00:22:00,104
The one you must meet isn't the King,

295
00:22:00,664 --> 00:22:03,884
but it's Prince Wang Wook.

296
00:22:05,104 --> 00:22:06,604
He's the next in line,

297
00:22:07,304 --> 00:22:13,014
and the noblemen and I support him.

298
00:22:13,344 --> 00:22:15,204
Is that so?

299
00:22:21,244 --> 00:22:25,084
He'll be the new King
of the central districts.

300
00:22:26,204 --> 00:22:28,884
Make him one of your men.

301
00:22:49,344 --> 00:22:52,484
Do you know Chunghae Trading Co.?

302
00:22:55,524 --> 00:22:58,394
You're asking for Chunghae
Trading Co. again?

303
00:22:58,584 --> 00:22:59,564
Father.

304
00:23:00,604 --> 00:23:02,804
It was a trading company in Gaebong,

305
00:23:03,484 --> 00:23:06,974
but 5 years ago, the assistant
head of the company

306
00:23:06,974 --> 00:23:08,964
and General Gwak were arranged to wed.

307
00:23:09,904 --> 00:23:14,124
But the assistant head
married a Goryeo man,

308
00:23:14,674 --> 00:23:16,974
and she went to Goryeo with him.

309
00:23:21,104 --> 00:23:22,324
Your Highness.

310
00:23:22,684 --> 00:23:26,424
She's already married.

311
00:23:27,024 --> 00:23:30,394
And 5 years ago, too.

312
00:23:32,524 --> 00:23:36,004
Isn't she absurd?

313
00:23:36,534 --> 00:23:41,644
How could brothers
fight over one woman?

314
00:23:45,104 --> 00:23:49,584
That assistant head was
a magnificent woman.

315
00:23:52,204 --> 00:23:56,144
I heard she established
a company in Goryeo.

316
00:23:57,284 --> 00:23:59,124
Have you heard of it?

317
00:24:00,804 --> 00:24:02,724
Of course I have.

318
00:24:04,004 --> 00:24:08,064
Prince Wang Wook knows about it well.

319
00:24:09,004 --> 00:24:10,564
You can ask him about the details.

320
00:24:18,904 --> 00:24:23,224
Is the assistant head still doing well

321
00:24:23,784 --> 00:24:25,444
with that Goryeo man?

322
00:24:29,604 --> 00:24:33,454
We shall talk about this again later.

323
00:24:51,104 --> 00:24:53,534
Could I disturb you for one moment?

324
00:24:57,044 --> 00:24:59,144
After what Wang Sik Ryeom said,

325
00:24:59,144 --> 00:25:02,184
you must be close with
the assistant head?

326
00:25:02,924 --> 00:25:07,284
Have you seen her Goryeo husband?

327
00:25:08,184 --> 00:25:10,404
He was ragged looking,

328
00:25:10,964 --> 00:25:13,224
but the look in his eyes and his spirit

329
00:25:13,224 --> 00:25:15,344
was like that of a tiger.

330
00:25:16,104 --> 00:25:18,694
I was disappointed to have lost her,

331
00:25:19,824 --> 00:25:25,704
but I understand why she chose that man.

332
00:25:27,084 --> 00:25:29,004
Wang Sik Ryeom mentioned

333
00:25:29,004 --> 00:25:33,014
that brothers fought over one woman.

334
00:25:33,324 --> 00:25:35,104
What does that mean?

335
00:25:57,084 --> 00:25:58,004
Sit down.

336
00:25:58,384 --> 00:26:02,324
Chunghae Trading Co. is not involved
in the move to the west anymore.

337
00:26:02,724 --> 00:26:04,004
What brings you here?

338
00:26:04,324 --> 00:26:06,484
I have something to ask you.

339
00:26:07,184 --> 00:26:08,244
Sit down.

340
00:26:13,724 --> 00:26:14,914
Please go ahead.

341
00:26:16,244 --> 00:26:17,224
Have you

342
00:26:19,004 --> 00:26:23,244
ever been married?

343
00:26:27,544 --> 00:26:29,444
What are you talking about?

344
00:26:30,124 --> 00:26:32,504
Why do you talk of
a marriage, all of a sudden?

345
00:26:32,504 --> 00:26:34,064
<i>If she was married,

346
00:26:34,764 --> 00:26:36,674
<i>she wouldn't not talk about it.

347
00:26:37,324 --> 00:26:38,724
<i>There has to be a reason

348
00:26:38,724 --> 00:26:40,424
<i>she can't talk about her marriage.

349
00:26:42,124 --> 00:26:44,104
<i>It's because the identity
of that Goryeo man

350
00:26:44,684 --> 00:26:46,844
<i>can't be revealed.

351
00:26:49,104 --> 00:26:50,084
<i>Could it be?

352
00:26:57,304 --> 00:26:58,544
I understand.

353
00:27:00,004 --> 00:27:03,604
We've talked about marriage before.

354
00:27:05,604 --> 00:27:07,284
I've asked an unnecessary question.

355
00:27:09,344 --> 00:27:10,324
I'll be leaving.

356
00:28:41,224 --> 00:28:42,924
It was a difference in temperature.

357
00:28:43,844 --> 00:28:45,104
A difference in temperature.

358
00:29:43,544 --> 00:29:45,444
I've found evidence.

359
00:29:46,244 --> 00:29:47,904
I'll reveal it at the great meeting

360
00:29:47,904 --> 00:29:49,664
and let the world know!

361
00:29:49,664 --> 00:29:52,984
Wang Sik Ryeom is leading the meeting.

