00:29:59,224 --> 00:30:01,524
That way the bronze mirror
will be recognized

365
00:30:01,524 --> 00:30:03,044
as evidence.

366
00:30:03,684 --> 00:30:06,204
If Wang Sik Ryeom leads the meeting,

367
00:30:06,204 --> 00:30:08,074
he might try to find
faults in the evidence.

368
00:30:08,964 --> 00:30:10,684
Thus the most important thing is

369
00:30:11,164 --> 00:30:12,964
to find the antidote.

370
00:30:13,544 --> 00:30:17,214
The antidote that Wang Wook has.

371
00:30:28,864 --> 00:30:30,124
Five years ago,

372
00:30:31,964 --> 00:30:34,504
was that the man

373
00:30:36,784 --> 00:30:38,184
who wed the assistant head?

374
00:30:42,404 --> 00:30:44,104
Yes, that's right.

375
00:30:44,944 --> 00:30:47,014
But considering his appearance,

376
00:30:47,014 --> 00:30:48,944
he must be of the royal family.

377
00:30:49,824 --> 00:30:52,084
Brothers, I see.

378
00:30:55,044 --> 00:30:56,744
I have a favor to ask of you.

379
00:31:03,204 --> 00:31:05,104
Please don't reveal to anyone

380
00:31:08,804 --> 00:31:10,904
about this marriage.

381
00:31:12,444 --> 00:31:14,864
That means erasing all memories

382
00:31:16,864 --> 00:31:20,644
related to the assistant head.

383
00:31:22,744 --> 00:31:23,964
Then

384
00:31:28,604 --> 00:31:30,284
when I become King,

385
00:31:33,324 --> 00:31:34,994
I'll repay you.

386
00:31:39,264 --> 00:31:43,344
I'm very greedy.

387
00:31:43,684 --> 00:31:44,984
I'll give you

388
00:31:47,824 --> 00:31:49,044
anything you want.

389
00:32:02,144 --> 00:32:03,444
It's you.

390
00:32:08,224 --> 00:32:09,104
Here.

391
00:32:22,564 --> 00:32:25,404
Soon the great meeting will take place.

392
00:32:25,824 --> 00:32:27,044
So?

393
00:32:27,044 --> 00:32:28,884
I have all of the evidence

394
00:32:28,884 --> 00:32:31,604
to punish Wang Sik Ryeom.

395
00:32:33,144 --> 00:32:35,454
I'll reveal it during
the great meeting,

396
00:32:35,844 --> 00:32:38,024
and then the whole world know.

397
00:32:38,544 --> 00:32:41,394
Then I'll remove him from his position

398
00:32:41,964 --> 00:32:43,564
and punish him.

399
00:32:45,324 --> 00:32:46,684
In order to do that,

400
00:32:47,704 --> 00:32:52,004
the King must lead the great meeting.

401
00:32:53,164 --> 00:32:58,504
Wook, try to change the fate of Goryeo

402
00:32:59,304 --> 00:33:01,664
with me, your own brother.

403
00:33:02,844 --> 00:33:04,684
Please give me the antidote.

404
00:33:07,484 --> 00:33:09,324
<i>If the marriage is found out,

405
00:33:09,804 --> 00:33:11,964
<i>Shin Yool will die.

406
00:33:12,684 --> 00:33:14,504
<i>How will you protect her?

407
00:33:15,244 --> 00:33:17,244
<i>How will you save her?

408
00:33:24,304 --> 00:33:25,504
Wook.

409
00:33:26,784 --> 00:33:28,104
It's the last chance.

410
00:33:29,484 --> 00:33:31,504
It's the last chance to stop the war

411
00:33:32,144 --> 00:33:34,864
between the royal family,

412
00:33:34,864 --> 00:33:38,404
so that everyone can live humanely!

413
00:33:41,464 --> 00:33:43,504
It's the last chance.

414
00:33:56,644 --> 00:33:58,744
Please take my hand.

415
00:34:01,044 --> 00:34:05,124
<i>The antidote is the last opportunity

416
00:34:05,764 --> 00:34:07,644
<i>to save Shin Yool.

417
00:34:10,464 --> 00:34:15,004
The hand I should take isn't yours.

418
00:34:55,654 --> 00:34:57,684
You must show your respect

419
00:34:58,704 --> 00:35:00,684
to Prince Wang Wook

420
00:35:01,224 --> 00:35:03,864
when you're in front of other people.

421
00:35:04,884 --> 00:35:08,344
He's the one who'll be King.

422
00:35:09,164 --> 00:35:11,604
Don't trust Wook that much.

423
00:35:11,604 --> 00:35:12,904
The way I see it,

424
00:35:12,904 --> 00:35:15,964
I don't think he'll
stay loyal to you.

425
00:35:18,464 --> 00:35:19,664
Poong.

426
00:35:20,464 --> 00:35:22,664
Loyalty, you see,

427
00:35:23,304 --> 00:35:28,324
depends on what I have
against the opponent.

428
00:35:30,104 --> 00:35:31,544
Wook has no choice

429
00:35:32,604 --> 00:35:37,364
to be loyal to me

430
00:35:38,364 --> 00:35:41,844
until the assistant head is dead.

431
00:35:41,844 --> 00:35:46,924
Wook has been bewitched by that woman?

432
00:35:48,524 --> 00:35:50,374
What kind of woman is she?

433
00:35:50,374 --> 00:35:52,784
She's an impudent woman.

434
00:35:54,104 --> 00:35:56,024
Don't keep her close to you.

435
00:35:56,624 --> 00:35:59,614
That makes her more interesting.

436
00:35:59,614 --> 00:36:00,944
Don't you dare!

437
00:36:04,004 --> 00:36:07,554
The problem right now isn't Wook,

438
00:36:07,924 --> 00:36:09,124
but So.

439
00:36:11,964 --> 00:36:14,804
He meddles in everything I do,

440
00:36:14,804 --> 00:36:17,464
and now he's trying to take my life?

441
00:36:17,464 --> 00:36:20,184
So why did you stand idle?

442
00:36:20,734 --> 00:36:22,024
You must kill him.

443
00:36:22,844 --> 00:36:24,804
The best defense is to attack.

444
00:36:24,804 --> 00:36:26,544
That attack needs a deadly weapon

445
00:36:27,644 --> 00:36:31,544
that will destroy the enemy instantly

446
00:36:31,544 --> 00:36:36,144
in order to gain victory.

447
00:36:40,384 --> 00:36:41,864
I'm looking for it.

448
00:36:42,584 --> 00:36:46,984
I'm looking for a deadly weapon

449
00:36:46,984 --> 00:36:49,224
to destroy Wang So!

450
00:36:51,624 --> 00:36:53,044
Why are you alone?

451
00:36:53,804 --> 00:36:56,304
I had to go somewhere.

452
00:36:57,924 --> 00:37:00,444
- Was it Chunghae Trading Co.?
- Yes.

453
00:37:00,984 --> 00:37:01,844
Yes.

454
00:37:02,124 --> 00:37:04,474
Did you meet that woman?

455
00:37:05,564 --> 00:37:09,114
What did she say when she saw you?

456
00:37:14,464 --> 00:37:15,584
Now.

457
00:37:15,944 --> 00:37:21,594
Let's talk about our
offers to one another.

458
00:37:22,184 --> 00:37:23,034
Sure.

459
00:37:25,184 --> 00:37:26,644
Leave us now.

460
00:37:42,484 --> 00:37:47,064
What can you offer me?

461
00:37:48,664 --> 00:37:50,204
Before that,

462
00:37:51,484 --> 00:37:53,424
I have something to ask you.

463
00:37:54,704 --> 00:37:56,004
Before,

464
00:37:56,004 --> 00:38:01,124
you said that two brothers
fought over one woman.

465
00:38:02,324 --> 00:38:06,644
Is one of those brothers
Prince Wang Wook

466
00:38:07,624 --> 00:38:09,184
and the other…?

467
00:38:21,044 --> 00:38:22,344
It's So.

468
00:38:23,584 --> 00:38:24,924
It's a man named Wang So.

469
00:38:28,104 --> 00:38:29,284
Wang So.

470
00:38:33,464 --> 00:38:38,904
It a letter saying that
the King hasn't improved.

471
00:38:40,184 --> 00:38:42,944
The great meeting is
right around the corner.

472
00:38:44,064 --> 00:38:46,214
Is there really no other way?

473
00:38:49,724 --> 00:38:51,544
Princess Yeo Won.

474
00:38:53,764 --> 00:38:56,504
She's given me her sincerity.

475
00:38:57,024 --> 00:38:59,754
I've given her my sincerity as well.

476
00:39:00,224 --> 00:39:02,724
If we still can't save him,

477
00:39:04,024 --> 00:39:06,964
then I must take action myself.

478
00:39:06,964 --> 00:39:08,184
You can't.

479
00:39:09,524 --> 00:39:12,124
The evidence we've
gathered for 5 years

480
00:39:12,124 --> 00:39:13,764
could all go to waste.

481
00:39:15,344 --> 00:39:17,244
Don't worry, Eun Chun.

482
00:39:19,244 --> 00:39:21,804
I will win, no matter what.

483
00:40:28,964 --> 00:40:30,244
This won't do.

484
00:40:31,864 --> 00:40:33,704
I can't provide soldiers for you

485
00:40:33,704 --> 00:40:36,084
with that offer.

486
00:40:36,684 --> 00:40:38,254
Come on.

487
00:40:38,884 --> 00:40:40,064
Wait.

488
00:40:42,804 --> 00:40:45,304
If I tell you an interesting story,

489
00:40:46,444 --> 00:40:48,494
will you fulfill my request?

490
00:40:58,744 --> 00:40:59,964
Don't forget

491
00:41:01,224 --> 00:41:02,444
the promise you made with me.

492
00:41:02,884 --> 00:41:08,024
I don't forget promises,
Your Highness.

493
00:41:31,584 --> 00:41:34,484
This man, this man!

494
00:41:47,684 --> 00:41:49,424
I heard you were looking for me.

495
00:41:51,304 --> 00:41:52,304
Yes.

496
00:41:52,984 --> 00:41:54,484
You're just as I've heard.

497
00:41:56,004 --> 00:41:58,444
Brothers would fight over you.

498
00:41:59,544 --> 00:42:00,504
Yes.

499
00:42:01,084 --> 00:42:04,404
Try to seduce me with your skills.

500
00:42:04,944 --> 00:42:06,534
What are you doing?

501
00:42:06,534 --> 00:42:07,934
What do you mean?

502
00:42:07,934 --> 00:42:09,204
I just want to play with you.

503
00:42:11,574 --> 00:42:12,574
What are you?

504
00:42:15,474 --> 00:42:16,384
Ouch!

505
00:42:16,384 --> 00:42:18,384
Let me go.

506
00:42:19,754 --> 00:42:22,284
Hey, let me go.

507
00:42:22,704 --> 00:42:24,424
Do you know who I am?

508
00:42:24,424 --> 00:42:26,424
I'm Wang Sik Ryeom's son, let me go!

509
00:42:29,944 --> 00:42:31,184
Gyeong!

510
00:42:31,484 --> 00:42:32,564
Come here!

511
00:42:39,964 --> 00:42:43,404
Did you just hit me, Prince Wang So?

512
00:42:51,624 --> 00:42:54,524
Next time, that'll be in your body.

513
00:42:55,664 --> 00:42:59,084
Poong, leave now.

514
00:43:28,744 --> 00:43:31,354
You could've just used your words.

515
00:43:32,864 --> 00:43:34,844
You have to treat people
like him like that,

516
00:43:34,844 --> 00:43:36,594
so that they won't
come back again.

517
00:43:38,264 --> 00:43:40,564
You must be in control of your temper.

518
00:43:40,924 --> 00:43:44,664
You said that I have fire above my head.

519
00:43:44,664 --> 00:43:47,764
It's not like I have a fire for a hat.

520
00:43:55,264 --> 00:43:59,084
Is the King doing well?

521
00:44:13,684 --> 00:44:16,784
I feel so tired, all of a sudden.

522
00:44:21,204 --> 00:44:22,204
Oh, boy.

523
00:44:24,584 --> 00:44:27,964
Oh, boy, I feel so
tired, all of a sudden.

524
00:45:03,604 --> 00:45:05,304
Don't worry.

525
00:45:07,204 --> 00:45:09,184
I'm trying.

526
00:45:12,024 --> 00:45:13,414
Do you need anything?

527
00:45:14,104 --> 00:45:14,984
You.

528
00:45:16,304 --> 00:45:19,594
You just need to be by my side.

529
00:45:20,944 --> 00:45:24,844
You're my greatest source of energy.

530
00:45:35,664 --> 00:45:36,944
Gaebong.

531
00:45:38,484 --> 00:45:40,014
Is Baek Myo gone?

532
00:45:49,984 --> 00:45:51,104
Did she leave?

533
00:46:04,884 --> 00:46:05,904
Thank you.

534
00:46:05,904 --> 00:46:08,244
It's not an antidote, per se.

535
00:46:09,204 --> 00:46:12,944
I obtained a medicinal
herb that's most similar

536
00:46:13,384 --> 00:46:15,144
and I've made the antidote.

537
00:46:15,784 --> 00:46:17,544
But you should only expect

538
00:46:17,544 --> 00:46:20,114
