of the poison.

539
00:46:20,404 --> 00:46:22,084
Thank you so much.

540
00:46:31,124 --> 00:46:33,384
It's already been 15 days

541
00:46:33,384 --> 00:46:35,104
since he last left his room.

542
00:46:35,584 --> 00:46:38,764
He must attend
the great meeting tomorrow.

543
00:46:39,764 --> 00:46:41,344
I'm worried.

544
00:46:41,344 --> 00:46:44,784
I'll be with him until the meeting,

545
00:46:44,784 --> 00:46:46,524
and I'll escort him there.

